# Feature Overview

## Logging (Voice Input)
- Trigger Whisper via mic button
- Output parsed as `{ movement, weight, reps }`
- Save into today's TinyBase log

## Generated Workouts
- Use selected focus (e.g., "chest")
- Call LLM with history context
- Output list of suggested movements with rep/weight ranges

## Progress Tracking
- Track per movement
- Volume, PR, 1RM estimates
- Show realistic strength curves

## Subscription Gating
- Logging: free
- Workout gen & stats: premium
